title: S17 Ep2: Supernatural News/Parashare: Attack of the Blue Meanie Edition
itunes:title: Supernatural News/Parashare: Attack of the Blue Meanie Edition
description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/Parashare: Attack of the Blue Meanie Edition with ECW/WWE Superstar The Blue Meanie!! 

Darkness Radio starts off it's 17th year and the year 2022 with some strange and bizarre stories this week!  Not only are UFO sightings on the rise, but Japan has built a hotel and other extras to welcome the extraterrestrials!  We give you three stories that will finally convince you that A.I. is taking over our civilization and trying to destroy you!  and it's time for us all to avenge Pluto !

Be sure to check out Blue Meanie's podcast, Mind of The Meanie wherever you get your podcasts!

Check out the Blue Meanie's store at Pro Wrestling Tees: https://www.prowrestlingtees.com/bluemeanie
